Author: Christina Eve
Content: Seriously, people, I love the healing foods and info on what ails us, but this is not justice.  This feels empty because it is empty. They want you to accept crumbs and play games so that no one steps into their true power and chooses to make moral choices and destroy evil people in life as they are living, in front of everyone so that we all Know.  Can't have morality running the day and making the super hard  choices though.   No way.  That might actually work to ease suffering more than hoping and praying, and they do not want people to know that.  There is deep satisfaction seeing ones enemy die and they keep that sense of satisfaction from our souls and give us imagination justice instead.  The dumbing down of society happens in many ways.

Content: Since I learned what happened to all the children worldwide, I feel personally hurt by the demons who hurt the children. Also use the light rods so much and when they are too many, I ask the unknown angels to help out. 🤗 I really hope that we will learn so much more about it soon. Thank you so much for sharing the information with us and giving us the tools to be in service of humanity 🙏🏼
